# Adds these pieces of the 2.12 patch 08 (media_core):
#
#   1. Uncomment `#include <pjmedia/vid_tee.h>` and add
#      `#include <pjmedia/transport_zrtp.h>` in pjmedia.h.
#   2. Add PJMEDIA_EVENT_KEYFRAME_REQUESTED to the pjmedia_event_type
#      enum in pjmedia/event.h.
#   3. Declare pjmedia_snd_port_reset_ec_state (stubbed) and
#      pjmedia_mixer_port_create (real impl, ported from 2.12).
#   4. New file sound_port_stubs.c with the stubs/real impls above.
#   5. Makefile additions for sound_port_stubs.o, transport_zrtp.o,
#      vid_tee.o.
#
# pjmedia_vid_dev_fb_set_callback stub previously lived here as well;
# it has been removed now that patch 06 (video_device) ports the real
# fb_dev.c which defines this function (would otherwise be a duplicate
# symbol at link time).
#
